### Internal ingest (NOT under /api, uses x-internal-secret header)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/iot-alerts
Content-Type: application/json
x-internal-secret: {{internalSecret}}

{
  "deviceIdentifier": "ESP32-001",
  "detectionType": "WILDLIFE_DISTURBANCE",
  "confidence": 0.94,
  "evidenceS3Key": "iot-evidence/2026-04-16/test-frame.jpg",
  "detectedAt": "2026-04-16T10:00:00.000Z"
}

###

### List IoT alerts (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/iot-alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get a single alert (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/iot-alerts/{{alertId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Flag as CONFIRMED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/iot-alerts/{{alertId}}/flag
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}

###

### Flag as FALSE_DETECTION
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/iot-alerts/{{alertId}}/flag
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "FALSE_DETECTION"
}
